Email Draft:


A new version of the JLab software libraries is available.  Version 1.3.1 include these updates:

- QT:           5.3.2
- geant4:       4.10.00.p03 > 4.10.01.p03
- gemc:         2.2  >  2.4
- JANA:         0.7.2  > 0.7.4p2
- banks:        1.0 > 1,2
- build system: 1.2 > 1.3
- ROOT:         5.34.21 > 5.34.34
- EVIO:         4.0 > 4.4.4
- CCDB:         1.03 > 1.06

The "production.csh", currently pointing at 1.2, will be updated next Tuesday, July 12th to point to 1.3.1.


Details on what's in each version can be found here.

To setup the environment:

source /site/12gev_phys/production.csh

An optional argument will select a particular version of the libraries. Availables choices are:

- 1.0
- 1.1
- 1.2
- 1.3
- 1.3.1
- devel


Attached is the versionining document.

Notice that the current "devel" includes ROOT6, which grant a "major" in the next release numbering, which will be 2.0 then.

Send questions/comments to ungaro@jlab.org, or to helpdesk@jlab.org.
Please also visit the Physics software documentation at http://data.jlab.org.


